name: 02. WRATH
description:
2/7 from “7 Deadly Sins” collection.

If you ask me what I feel, what a tough time, I am well aware of what I get when between my teeth I think. Give me strength for the challange to stay on the right path, for I long to get far, where desires fly, dizziness from fears, and loved ones who go away. For the time being I would advise you: what is yours do not let go, may you see it for now, may you see it forever. If you can bear it, it is because you want to, and you weep convincingly. You feel sorry between the walnut protected by its shell.
